  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694150/extras/a6de29bd6d22db3b9108a2ae20ec2031.avif?t=1662030173\" width=591 height=84 /></span><br>One day, the kingdom wakes up to a morning in which all inner chambers' gates are locked and their keys vanish. The kingdom chooses the Lancelot to find all keys and unlock all locked gates. As the Lancelot, use the crates and solve the puzzles for unlocking all the gates.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694150/extras/0a1772f638e251be7ac8f98e8c5387f2.avif?t=1662030173\" width=591 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694150/extras/0680abd7a190a9472c180eb2a9b1722c.poster.avif?t=1662030173\" width=586 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694150/extras/0680abd7a190a9472c180eb2a9b1722c.webm?t=1662030173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694150/extras/0680abd7a190a9472c180eb2a9b1722c.mp4?t=1662030173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- Play through 25 unique stages.<br>- Physics based puzzles.<br>- Challenging collectables to collect.<br>- Multiple methods to solve each puzzle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694150/extras/f7b8626aae2c18c219192f9902d03516.avif?t=1662030173\" width=591 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694150/extras/c59265540dd936a05b92d21705804b10.poster.avif?t=1662030173\" width=586 he